description:
It's been quite some time since Will Braun and Carter Woods last saw each other, but as soon as Carter opens the door to find him standing there, the sparks fly and it's like they were never separated. Will wonders if he should grab his stuff from the car but Carter is in too much of a hurry to mess with any of that right now. All he can think of is rushing Will to the bedroom and having his way with him. Will has crossed the country to make this moment happen, so he's had plenty of time to wait. Now that Carter's in front of him, he agrees there's no time like the present to finally satisfy the long distance lust that has been building in the both of them since they last were together.

Enjoy!
title: Cross Country Cock
